<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The portal also supports services like patta and chitta search, guideline value checking, stamp duty details, and access to certificates for births, deaths, marriages, firms, and chit funds. With its digital system, TNREGINET improves transparency, saves time, and helps residents across Tamil Nadu handle property and legal matters more conveniently from home.</p>


