<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_0f6015-74"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading10_c3e73f-94 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_c3e73f-94"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">What is TNREGINET?</span></h2></div></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://tnreginetportaal.com/2026/01/23/guide-for-beginners/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">TNREGINET</a> is the official e-governance portal of the Tamil Nadu Government, created to simplify property and document-related services for citizens. It allows users to access important services online, including property registration, marriage and birth registration, encumbrance certificate applications, stamp duty details, patta and chitta services, and guideline value searches, reducing the need to visit government offices in person.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Managed by the Inspector General of Registration (IGRS), the portal is designed to make registration processes faster, more transparent, and more convenient for people across Tamil Nadu. It also supports services related to death registration, chit funds, and business registrations, helping citizens handle legal and property matters securely and efficiently from home.</p>



