<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_596f5f-9f"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>You’ll receive an OTP (One-Time Password) on your registered mobile or email.</li>



<li>Enter the OTP to verify your details.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

</div></div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_89fca0-a9" data-aos="slide-right" data-aos-duration="950"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><div class="kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id10_09b3c6-b9 alignnone wp-block-kadence-rowlayout"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-2-columns kt-row-layout-row kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-mobile-layout-row kt-row-valign-top">

<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_7b0cbe-65"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_93ee7b-a3 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette3-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_93ee7b-a3"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Complete Registration</strong></span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_5770c0-4d"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li class="has-theme-palette-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-c6d9aea73e4c7812db7b1faad1f60c00">After verification, click on “<strong>Complete Registration</strong>” to finish the process.</li>



<li>आप जानकारी डाउनलोड भी कर सकते हैं, अगर आक इसकी जरूरत हो।</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

</div></div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_d48c20-d6"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Login to Start Using Services</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Once your account is created, log in with your username and password.</li>



<li>You can now access services like EC view, patta chitta, marriage registration, and more.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>

</div></div>

