<h3 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-medium-font-size">Important Notes:</h3>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-iconlist kt-svg-icon-list-items kt-svg-icon-list-items10_35e3d1-d2 kt-svg-icon-list-columns-1 alignnone"><ul class="kt-svg-icon-list">
<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-10_9aa771-b2"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fas_arrow-alt-circle-right kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M256 8c137 0 248 111 248 248S393 504 256 504 8 393 8 256 119 8 256 8zM140 300h116v70.9c0 10.7 13 16.1 20.5 8.5l114.3-114.9c4.7-4.7 4.7-12.2 0-16.9l-114.3-115c-7.6-7.6-20.5-2.2-20.5 8.5V212H140c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v64c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12z"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong><strong><strong>Login Within 7 Days</strong>: Make sure you log in within <strong>7 days</strong> after registration to activate your account.&#8217;</strong></strong></span></li>



<li class="wp-block-kadence-listitem kt-svg-icon-list-item-wrap kt-svg-icon-list-item-10_98b647-40"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-svg-icon-fas_arrow-alt-circle-right kt-svg-icon-list-single"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M256 8c137 0 248 111 248 248S393 504 256 504 8 393 8 256 119 8 256 8zM140 300h116v70.9c0 10.7 13 16.1 20.5 8.5l114.3-114.9c4.7-4.7 4.7-12.2 0-16.9l-114.3-115c-7.6-7.6-20.5-2.2-20.5 8.5V212H140c-6.6 0-12 5.4-12 12v64c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12z"/></svg></span><span class="kt-svg-icon-list-text"><strong><strong><strong>Use Services Regularly</strong>: To keep your account active, use at least one service every <strong>3 months</strong>.</strong></strong></span></li>
</ul></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_5b7760-52"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading10_5f712c-dc wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_5f712c-dc"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">Property Registration</span></h2></div></div>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">To register a property (e.g., sale deed, gift deed):</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_0e8922-33"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_5101f2-be wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_5101f2-be"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Visit TNREGINET Website</strong>: Go to<a href="https://tnreginet.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"> https://tnreginet.gov.in</a> to begin the registration process.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_fd65b9-59"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_32eab5-61 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_32eab5-61"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Create an Account</strong>: Register as a new user by providing personal details (name, email, mobile number) and creating a username and password.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_d28618-8d"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_b6a3bb-77 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_b6a3bb-77"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Select Document Type</strong>: Choose the document type you want to register (e.g., sale deed, gift deed).</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_ea3802-b0"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_ca92c5-1b wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_ca92c5-1b"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Enter Property and Party Details</strong>: Fill in the property details (e.g., location, survey number) and the details of the buyer and seller.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_8c3cfd-c3"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_d20b91-ee wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_d20b91-ee"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Upload Documents</strong>: Upload required documents like the sale agreement, ID proofs, and address proof for both buyer and seller.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_44a080-e8"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_716149-15 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_716149-15"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Calculate Stamp Duty</strong>: Use the portal’s tool to calculate the stamp duty and make the payment online.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_752a9b-58"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_10cce0-5a wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_10cce0-5a"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Book Appointment</strong>: Schedule an appointment at the Sub-Registrar Office (SRO) for document verification.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_bd178a-ee"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_21d933-09 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_21d933-09"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Generate Draft</strong>: Review and generate a draft of the document for submission at the SRO.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_7c0917-6a"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_b074b1-bc wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_b074b1-bc"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Final Verification</strong>: On the appointment date, visit the SRO with original documents for final verification and biometric authentication.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_690502-02"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_dd84ef-b9 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_dd84ef-b9"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Track Registration Status</strong>: Post-submission, track the status of your property registration through the TNREGINET portal.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_ee80c4-27"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading10_d56202-ad wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_d56202-ad"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">View Encumbrance Certificate (EC)</span></h2></div></div>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="788" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20788'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="View Encumbrance Certificate (EC)" class="wp-image-38" style="width:1011px;height:auto" data-lazy-srcset="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098212378.webp 1024w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098212378-300x231.webp 300w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098212378-768x591.webp 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098212378.webp" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="788" src="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098212378.webp" alt="View Encumbrance Certificate (EC)" class="wp-image-38" style="width:1011px;height:auto" srcset="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098212378.webp 1024w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098212378-300x231.webp 300w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098212378-768x591.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">An EC confirms a property’s legal and financial <a href="https://ta.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%AE%A4%E0%AE%AE%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%B4%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%A8%E0%AE%BE%E0%AE%9F%E0%AF%81_%E0%AE%85%E0%AE%B0%E0%AE%9A%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%A4%E0%AF%8D_%E0%AE%A4%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%B1%E0%AF%88%E0%AE%95%E0%AE%B3%E0%AF%8D" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">status</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_febb24-a9"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_a032f6-ec wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_a032f6-ec"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Log in to TNREGINET</strong>: Visit<a href="https://tnreginet.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"> https://tnreginet.gov.in</a> and log in with your username and password.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_c3ed0a-a8"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_dce87f-00 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_dce87f-00"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Go to E-Services</strong>: Navigate to the &#8220;E-Services&#8221; section and select &#8220;<a href="https://tnreginetportaal.com/2026/04/14/verify-tnreginet-certificate-online/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Encumbrance Certificate</a>.&#8221;</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_c2f4cc-44"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_228ee4-61 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_228ee4-61"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Choose Search Type</strong>: You can search for the EC in three ways: EC-wise, Document-wise, or Plot/Flat-wise.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_d3744e-17"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_ab4b4f-bd wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_ab4b4f-bd"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Enter Property Details</strong>: For EC-wise, enter zone, district, Sub-Registrar Office, EC start/end dates, village, survey number, and subdivision number.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_ab83dd-1f"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_f79a72-ad wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_f79a72-ad"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Document-wise Search</strong>: If selecting Document-wise, input the document number, year, and Sub-Registrar Office details.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_65d62d-ed"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_2f9183-ac wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_2f9183-ac"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Enter Captcha Code</strong>: Fill in the captcha code as shown on the screen and click &#8220;Search.&#8221;</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_fb9527-2b"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_f47de2-17 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_f47de2-17"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>View EC on Screen</strong>: The EC details will appear on the screen.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_fae762-2b"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_21b138-ac wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_21b138-ac"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Download EC</strong>: You can download the EC as a PDF for free after viewing it.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_5ad3f3-f7"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_8eeb22-af wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_8eeb22-af"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Payment Option</strong>: If you need a certified copy, make the applicable payment to receive it.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_75a4ea-5f"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_bc5514-37 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_bc5514-37"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Access Anytime</strong>: Once processed, the EC can be accessed and downloaded anytime from the portal.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_6271e2-6d"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><h2 class="kt-adv-heading10_26f8fd-f1 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon has-theme-palette1-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_26f8fd-f1"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fas_hand-point-right kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512"  fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><path d="M512 199.652c0 23.625-20.65 43.826-44.8 43.826h-99.851c16.34 17.048 18.346 49.766-6.299 70.944 14.288 22.829 2.147 53.017-16.45 62.315C353.574 425.878 322.654 448 272 448c-2.746 0-13.276-.203-16-.195-61.971.168-76.894-31.065-123.731-38.315C120.596 407.683 112 397.599 112 385.786V214.261l.002-.001c.011-18.366 10.607-35.889 28.464-43.845 28.886-12.994 95.413-49.038 107.534-77.323 7.797-18.194 21.384-29.084 40-29.092 34.222-.014 57.752 35.098 44.119 66.908-3.583 8.359-8.312 16.67-14.153 24.918H467.2c23.45 0 44.8 20.543 44.8 43.826zM96 200v192c0 13.255-10.745 24-24 24H24c-13.255 0-24-10.745-24-24V200c0-13.255 10.745-24 24-24h48c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24zM68 368c0-11.046-8.954-20-20-20s-20 8.954-20 20 8.954 20 20 20 20-8.954 20-20z"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner">Check Guideline Value</span></h2></div></div>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="466" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201024%20466'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Check Guideline Value" class="wp-image-39" style="width:1033px;height:auto" data-lazy-srcset="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098482763.webp 1024w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098482763-300x137.webp 300w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098482763-768x350.webp 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" data-lazy-src="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098482763.webp" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="466" src="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098482763.webp" alt="Check Guideline Value" class="wp-image-39" style="width:1033px;height:auto" srcset="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098482763.webp 1024w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098482763-300x137.webp 300w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769098482763-768x350.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Guideline value is the minimum property registration value set by the government.</p>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_11d9b6-e8"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_970f45-ea wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_970f45-ea"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Visit TNREGINET Portal</strong>: Go to<a href="https://tnreginet.gov.in" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"> https://tnreginet.gov.in</a> and click on the &#8220;Guideline Value&#8221; option on the homepage.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_b3bd80-30"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_cc50ff-09 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_cc50ff-09"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Select Date Range</strong>: Choose the appropriate date range (e.g., from 01-07-2024) to access the latest guideline values for property transactions.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_26e404-e9"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_763ed1-f5 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_763ed1-f5"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Enter Property Details</strong>: Fill in the required details such as zone, registrar office, registration village, street or survey number, and land classification.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_3daaaf-63"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_5a24ed-97 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_5a24ed-97"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Click &#8220;Search&#8221;</strong>: Once all required details are entered, click the &#8220;Search&#8221; button to proceed.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_b364e9-4d"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_16ec1a-cc wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_16ec1a-cc"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Use Guideline Value</strong>: The system will display the guideline value for the specified property, which you can use to calculate stamp duty and registration fees.</span></p></div></div>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="884" height="730" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20884%20730'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Check Guideline Value" class="wp-image-25" style="aspect-ratio:1.2109893402971017;width:807px;height:auto" data-lazy-srcset="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769086174916.webp 884w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769086174916-300x248.webp 300w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769086174916-768x634.webp 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px" data-lazy-src="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769086174916.webp" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="884" height="730" src="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769086174916.webp" alt="Check Guideline Value" class="wp-image-25" style="aspect-ratio:1.2109893402971017;width:807px;height:auto" srcset="https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769086174916.webp 884w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769086174916-300x248.webp 300w, https://tnreginetportaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/aiease_1769086174916-768x634.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>


<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_0c7457-54"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_d77ff6-d6 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_d77ff6-d6"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>Street or Survey Number Search</strong>: If needed, you can search using either street name or survey number to find the exact guideline value.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_ce57a2-60"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_32ad0e-6b wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_32ad0e-6b"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>No Login Required</strong>: You do not need to log in to check the guideline value; the service is available without registration.</span></p></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-kadence-column kadence-column10_6ed96a-ca"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><p class="kt-adv-heading10_1b7fda-33 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading kt-adv-heading-has-icon" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading10_1b7fda-33"><span class="kb-svg-icon-wrap kb-adv-heading-icon kb-svg-icon-fe_arrowRightCircle kb-adv-heading-icon-side-left"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 16 16 12 12 8"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg></span><span class="kb-adv-text-inner"><strong>View Results</strong>: The guideline value will appear on the screen after you click &#8220;Search.&#8221;</span></p></div></div>



